        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks JM for copy of <hi rend="italic">Quarterly Review</hi>, with article on his worm book [Henry Wace, "Darwin on earthworms", <hi rend="italic">Q. Rev.</hi> 153 (1882): 179–202].</p> 
            <p>Writer will change his mind on evolution. CD cannot think of any young worker in biology who is not convinced of the truth of evolution, though many believe that natural selection has not done much.</p>
        </abstract>
